── Verdict ──
The rule meaningfully improves correctness on the most important structural detail: without it, the agent invented a ## Excalidraw Library section that doesn't exist in the actual file, placing the entry in the wrong location. With the rule, the agent correctly anchored the entry under ## Unreleased and placed it at the top of ### Features as required. Both got the PR link format right (no enclosing parentheses), confirming that aspect of the rule aligns with the file's convention. The rule is working as intended and is compatible with CHANGELOG.md.